org.crsh.cli.type

Class ValueType<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.crsh.cli.type.ValueType<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the generic value type

    public abstract class ValueType<V>
extends Object
    Defines a type for values, this is used for transforming a textual value into a type, for command argument and options. A value type defines:
    • The generic value type that is converted to.
    • The implementation of the parse(Class, String) method that transforms the string into a value.
    • An optional completer.
